_sText:
This map takes place outside in a city courtyard. There is a left and right side path for each team as well as a middle route. Each team has a center bunker that offers two levels of protection. Those bunkers have ramps that lead to the catwalk.

The catwalk circles the entire level and has two walks that lead to the rooftops in the middle of the map. Each team also has 1 ladder on their side that leads to the rooftop.

This version has Buy Zones for each team.  You can find the Gun Game version here:  http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/106919
